metadata.name: Black Betty
metadata.description: Meet the newest member of Zombie Tramp universe!\nBlack Betty has made a living killing the unkillable. She has taken down monsters of every shape and size with a style all her own. But when a man’s daughter is kidnapped by a local legend, Betty steps in to save her… for a price!\nIf you need it dead (and you’ve got the cash!), Betty’s your girl!
